title: XCOM.Enemy.Within.XBOX360 (j-TAG/RGH ONLY)
description:
PER REQUEST

THIS DOES NOT CONTAIN AN ISO. THIS IS A GAME RIP

The gameplay and plot of XCOM: Enemy Within is largely remains as same as XCOM: Enemy Unknown with some additional features. The player manages the XCOM headquarters in almost real time progress, but much of the gameplay consists of turn-based battles against the invading aliens and some with the rogue human faction EXALT across the globe. Similar to the numerous expansions of the Civilization series, the pack retains the core storyline but adds a broad variety of contents.
